#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FILE NAME:	Makefile
#
# DESCRIPTION:  Makefile for a C++ program
#
# PURPOSE:	Build a program executable on Linux
#
# MODIFICATION HISTORY:
#
# Author	       Date	    Modifications(s)
# -----------	       ---------    ----------------
# Michael Des Roches   2018-02-01   Version 1
